Ex-Big Brother Naija, BBNaija housemate, Gedoni Ekpata, has officially engaged his lover, Khafi. Gedoni popped the question on Christmas Day while the lovebirds were on a vacation in Cape Verde. Khafi disclosed this on her Instagram page even as fans bombarded her page with congratulatory messages. She wrote: “Oh and I got the best Christmas gift ever. I said Yes Mrs. Ekpata loafing.”  DAILY POST recalls that the BBNaija lovebirds, Gedoni and Khafi, had on different occasions during the 2019 BBNaija show caught in the house in cozy moments. Gedoni Ekpata had after his eviction reassured that his relationship with his love interest, Khafi Kareem was beyond the reality show. Download Daily Post App.    Subscribe to Daily Post Newsletter.    Advertise with us.   Send us enquiries, press releases.